<p class="ayah 31-3" id="3" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُدًى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">A guidance</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَرَحْمَةً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and a mercy</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِّلْمُحْسِنِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for the good-doers,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>3<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
