<p class="ayah 31-13" id="13" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِذْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">said</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لُقْمَـٰنُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Luqman</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِٱبْنِهِۦ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to his son</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَهُوَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">while he</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَعِظُهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(was) instructing him,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰبُنَىَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`O my son!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(Do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُشْرِكْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">associate partners</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱللَّهِ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with Allah.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلشِّرْكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">associating partners</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar qur