"ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱشْكُرْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Be grateful</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to Me</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلِوَٲلِدَيْكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and to your parents;</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَىَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">towards Me</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمَصِيرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) the destination.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>14<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
