<p class="ayah 31-16" id="16" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰبُنَىَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`O my son!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّهَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed it,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَكُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">it be</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِثْقَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) weight</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَبَّةٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) a grain</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَرْدَلٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a mustard seed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَتَكُن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and it be</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">صَخْرَةٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a rock</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en se