<span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and has subjected</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلشَّمْسَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the sun</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْقَمَرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the moon,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُلٌّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">each</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَجْرِىٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">moving</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَجَلٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a term</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُّسَمًّى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">appointed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَعْمَلُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you do</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَبِيرٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) All-Aware.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </